---
// State 1: Chat interaction
---
<div class="hero-state hero-state-1 hm-chat">
  <div class="hm-chat-header">
    <div class="hm-chat-avatar">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined">smart_toy</span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="hm-chat-name">Ilaaj AI Assistant</p>
      <p class="hm-chat-status">Online • AI Health Guide</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hm-messages">
    <div class="hm-msg">
      <div class="hm-bubble hm-bubble--ai">
        <p>Assalam-o-Alaikum! Aap kaise hain? Bataiye main aapki kya madad kar sakta hoon?</p>
      </div>
      <span class="hm-time hm-time--ai">10:02 AM</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hm-msg hm-msg--user">
      <div class="hm-bubble hm-bubble--user">
        <p>Walaikum Assalam. Mujhe kal raat se bukhar hai aur gala kharab hai.</p>
      </div>
      <span class="hm-time hm-time--user">10:03 AM</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hm-msg">
      <div class="hm-bubble hm-bubble--typing">
        <span>Analyzing symptoms</span>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:2px;margin-left:4px">
          <span class="typing-dot"></span>
          <span class="typing-dot"></span>
          <span class="typing-dot"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
